<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<!-- Created with Liquid Technologies Online Tools 1.0 (https://www.liquid-technologies.com) -->
<xs:schema attributeFormDefault="unqualified" elementFormDefault="qualified" xmlns:xs="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema">
  <xs:element name="person">
    <xs:complexType>
      <xs:sequence>
        <xs:element name="name" type="xs:string" />
        <xs:element name="age" type="xs:decimal" />
        <xs:element name="contacts">
          <xs:complexType>
            <xs:sequence>
              <xs:element maxOccurs="unbounded" name="contact">
                <xs:complexType>
                  <xs:sequence>
                    <xs:element name="type" type="xs:string" />
                    <xs:element name="value" type="xs:string" />
                  </xs:sequence>
                </xs:complexType>
              </xs:element>
            </xs:sequence>
          </xs:complexType>
        </xs:element>
        <xs:element name="address">
          <xs:complexType>
            <xs:sequence>
              <xs:element name="street" type="xs:string" />
              <xs:element name="city" type="xs:string" />
              <xs:element name="zipcode" type="xs:unsignedShort" />
              <xs:element name="history">
                <xs:complexType>
                  <xs:sequence>
                    <xs:element maxOccurs="unbounded" name="previous_address">
                      <xs:complexType>
                        <xs:sequence>
                          <xs:element name="previous_city" type="xs:string" />
                          <xs:element name="years" type="xs:unsignedByte" />
                        </xs:sequence>
                      </xs:complexType>
                    </xs:element>
                  </xs:sequence>
                </xs:complexType>
              </xs:element>
            </xs:sequence>
          </xs:complexType>
        </xs:element>
        <xs:element name="num">
          <xs:complexType>
            <xs:sequence>
              <xs:element maxOccurs="unbounded" name="n" type="xs:unsignedByte" />
            </xs:sequence>
          </xs:complexType>
        </xs:element>
      </xs:sequence>
    </xs:complexType>
  </xs:element>
</xs:schema>
